    dc:description "FIGURE 2 A – G. Gunabopicobia masalaje sp. nov., female (A – D). A, hypostomal apex with distal part of movable cheliceral digit; B, peritremes; C, solenidia of legs I; D, proximal part of movable cheliceral digit. Male (E – G). E, hypostomal apex with distal part of movable cheliceral digit; F, peritremes; G, genito-anal region." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231224/files/figure.png" ;
